        ScriptableObject: 
        Class: 
      Asset: {fileID: 0}
      Id: e8fd0db9-b29b-4c6a-bcd5-ca3c4b97e49b
      StepElements: []
    - Text: Install the Intro Sample and press play see the game running in offline
